ğŸ“Œ PART 5: BACKUP AND RESTORE
ğŸ”„ Backup:
All data is stored in:
~/uptime-kuma/uptime-kuma-data/
Back this up regularly using:
rsync -a ~/uptime-kuma/uptime-kuma-data /path/to/backup/
________________________________________
âœ… Restore:
Just restore the data folder to the same path, then start:
docker-compose up -d
